comments.content:
Hi, saravanakumar 
Thank you for reporting this case.

I would like to reproduce it. 
Can you help me with it ?

If you can provide steps to reproduce, it would be great .
I would like to create openstack installation with the same configuration as you had.

Few questions which I think can help me to reproduce your environment and reporeted situation:
What type of installation did you use ? How did you install openstack ? Did you use any specific installation instruction or/and automation ?
Can you please provide me some details about your configuration of nova services and other openstack services ( neutron, glance ) ?
